{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/setupautomation"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SetupAutomation"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SetupAutomation"},{"type":"text","text":" provides version-specific keyboard input sequences"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that walk through the macOS Setup Assistant without any human"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interaction. After the sequence completes, the VM has:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A user account (configurable, defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"admin"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"admin"},{"type":"text","text":")"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SSH (Remote Login) enabled"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A UTC timezone configured"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Design","type":"heading","anchor":"Design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This follows the approach pioneered by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/cirruslabs\/tart","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for Packer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"boot_command"},{"type":"text","text":" automation. The sequences have been verified against"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Tart’s working Packer plugin and adapted for direct use via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Virtualization framework’s keyboard API.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},